==Indonesian==
===Etymology===
Derived from the root '''''[[jalan]]'''''.
===Verb===
====Transitive====
'''menjalani'''

# to [[walk]] on ([[something]])
# to [[undergo]], to [[endure]]
# to go [[through]] (a [[period]] of your [[life]])
# to [[travel]] [[through]] [[somewhere]]
# to go [[along]] (a [[road]])

